{"id":309613,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/维权网-浙江慈溪千余警察强行征土地、抓捕多位/","date":"2013-08-20T13:48:39Z","modified":"2013-08-20T13:48:39Z","title":"维权网 | 浙江慈溪千余警察强行征土地、抓捕多位村民（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）</span>2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日，浙江省慈溪市胜山镇大湾村，约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1500</span><span>名特警、协警进村强行征地，并抓捕多名抗议村民。征地补偿都没谈好就动用特警清场抓人，强制填埋带有农作物的农田，村民无奈，有老人在征地现场洒泪，带着农具在田间地头进行最后的除草。</span></p>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<p><span>据村民反映，村里一户人家最多只剩二亩地了，政府提出的征地补偿为每亩</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4.5</span><span>万元，但转手却能卖出几倍甚至数十倍的价格。因当地政府征地赔偿价格过低，大湾村村民多次示威抵制政府强征，曾在今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月与上千警察对峙数天。</span></p>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-sQJnsHC89Ck/UhMte9oe3CI/AAAAAAAAnGc/XGhdJfwrgXM/s1600/1.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"257\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-sQJnsHC89Ck/UhMte9oe3CI/AAAAAAAAnGc/XGhdJfwrgXM/s400/1.JPG\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-tgcbTaov78M/UhMtfuRsv-I/AAAAAAAAnGk/DKDv_1FpUwA/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-tgcbTaov78M/UhMtfuRsv-I/AAAAAAAAnGk/DKDv_1FpUwA/s400/2.jpg\" width=\"357\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-mbHzXjB1ZDY/UhMtgrN_n1I/AAAAAAAAnGs/muKZ8UIO98s/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-mbHzXjB1ZDY/UhMtgrN_n1I/AAAAAAAAnGs/muKZ8UIO98s/s400/3.jpg\" width=\"355\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b